						<p>On a slab lying in Survey No. 117.</p>						

						<p>Circa 16th century.</p>						

						<p>It records the construction of a tank by the sons of <hi rend="italic">Sēnabōva</hi> Lakaṇa, who received a gift of land and house-site for the work done. The epigraph is damaged in the beginning.</p>						

